title: Taj Ali wins NA-225 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Peoples Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Sadiq Ali Memon has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-225 Thatta by securing 1,40,773 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz’s  Rasool Bux Jakhro , who bagged 28,899 votes.
Overall voters’ turnout remained 37.33 percent.
